General.Name: J.Jill Inc
General.Description: J.Jill, Inc. operates as an omnichannel retailer for women's apparel under the J.Jill brand in the United States. It offers casual wear, athletic wear, and loungewear; footwear; and accessories, including scarves and jewelry. The company markets its products through retail stores, website, and catalogs. The company was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Quincy, Massachusetts.
